<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">抚子 你的单人露营怎么样了</font>

1
00:00:08,075 --> 00:00:09,555
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">嗯 挺开心的</font>

2
00:00:10,185 --> 00:00:11,885
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">去富士宫观光</font>

3
00:00:12,335 --> 00:00:14,385
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">露营地的夜景也很美</font>

4
00:00:15,045 --> 00:00:17,125
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">晚饭也做得很成功</font>

5
00:00:19,075 --> 00:00:21,175
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">铝箔纸包烤看上去好棒呢</font>

6
00:00:21,775 --> 00:00:25,275
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不过 吃过晚饭之后还是有点闲</font>

7
00:00:27,425 --> 00:00:29,205
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">露营地没有信号</font>

8
00:00:29,375 --> 00:00:32,625
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我就一边赏夜景 一边发呆想事情</font>

9
00:00:35,425 --> 00:00:38,345
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">然后就又想和大家一起去露营了</font>

10
00:00:40,035 --> 00:00:40,765
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这样啊</font>

11
00:00:41,245 --> 00:00:43,305
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">今后 单人露营和团体露营</font>

12
00:00:43,405 --> 00:00:45,135
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我两个都想参加</font>

13
00:00:45,345 --> 00:00:46,405
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">原来如此</font>

14
00:00:46,995 --> 00:00:48,825
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那 下次就是团体露营啦</font>

15
00:00:50,095 --> 00:00:50,785
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是呀</font>

16
00:00:51,365 --> 00:00:53,355
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">也叫上小凛和惠那</font>

17
00:00:54,645 --> 00:00:56,945
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是自圣诞露营以来的全明星阵容啦</font>

18
00:00:57,365 --> 00:00:59,925
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">赶快去找老师商量</font>

19
00:01:13,845 --> 00:01:20,365
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">摇曳露营 第二季</font>

20
00:02:36,405 --> 00:02:39,765
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那就三月初去伊豆 怎么样
(冬日结束与出发之日)</font>

21
00:02:40,145 --> 00:02:41,625
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">伊豆露营啊</font>

22
00:02:41,935 --> 00:02:42,995
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">伊豆好啊</font>

23
00:02:43,275 --> 00:02:44,685
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是啊 好地方</font>

24
00:02:45,425 --> 00:02:47,505
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">冬天也比较温暖</font>

25
00:02:48,035 --> 00:02:51,745
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">也想去找在山中湖照顾过我们的饭田一家道谢</font>

26
00:02:52,505 --> 00:02:56,055
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">得带伴手礼 去感谢他们的帮助呢</font>

27
00:02:56,285 --> 00:02:57,055
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是啊</font>

28
00:02:57,875 --> 00:03:00,215
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">可是为什么要等一个多月呢</font>

29
00:03:00,695 --> 00:03:03,245
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">各位之前才刚去露营过吧</font>

30
00:03:03,825 --> 00:03:05,965
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">要去伊豆 路费也比较贵</font>

31
00:03:06,785 --> 00:03:09,165
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我觉得稍等一阵会比较好</font>

32
00:03:09,775 --> 00:03:12,865
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">确实 资金不足的问题无法否认</font>

33
00:03:13,075 --> 00:03:14,065
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是啊</font>

34
00:03:14,315 --> 00:03:16,315
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">也想多吃点好吃的呢</font>

35
00:03:16,985 --> 00:03:19,915
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">而且 2月末还有期末考试</font>

36
00:03:21,535 --> 00:03:22,735
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是吧 大垣同学</font>

37
00:03:22,985 --> 00:03:24,985
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">岌岌可危</font>

38
00:03:28,095 --> 00:03:30,285
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">已经和露营者打成一片啦</font>

39
00:03:31,435 --> 00:03:32,585
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不愧是抚子</font>

40
00:03:35,745 --> 00:03:37,645
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">野活组露营 in 伊豆
(伊豆欢迎你)</font>

41
00:03:38,005 --> 00:03:39,875
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">预定3月初举行哦</font>

42
00:03:40,185 --> 00:03:41,605
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">惠那和小凛要不要一起来</font>

43
00:03:42,005 --> 00:03:43,735
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好好打工赚钱 去伊豆露营呀</font>

44
00:03:43,985 --> 00:03:45,315
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">简直就是豪游</font>

45
00:03:45,895 --> 00:03:46,745
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">“豪游”</font>

46
00:03:47,085 --> 00:03:48,295
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好呀 去伊豆</font>

47
00:03:49,075 --> 00:03:51,505
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">说起来 凛本来新年要去的吧</font>

48
00:03:52,035 --> 00:03:54,525
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">嗯 但是听说人很多 我就放弃了</font>

49
00:03:55,645 --> 00:03:56,295
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">你怎么说</font>

50
00:03:59,475 --> 00:04:00,315
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">能去的话就去</font>

51
00:04:00,785 --> 00:04:02,665
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好 再次挑战伊豆</font>

52
00:04:04,185 --> 00:04:05,845
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那我差不多该去打工了</font>

53
00:04:06,235 --> 00:04:06,905
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好</font>

54
00:04:10,165 --> 00:04:10,745
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">对了</font>

55
00:04:11,925 --> 00:04:13,875
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">凛果然是个好人呢</font>

56
00:04:14,415 --> 00:04:17,845
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">担心抚子的安全 特地跑到露营地去</font>

57
00:04:19,525 --> 00:04:21,055
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">你 你怎么知道的</font>

58
00:04:22,625 --> 00:04:23,825
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">怎么知道的呢</font>

59
00:04:24,555 --> 00:04:26,035
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那明天见啦</font>

60
00:04:32,895 --> 00:04:33,905
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">她为什么会知道</font>

61
00:04:34,725 --> 00:04:35,995
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我明明没告诉别人</font>

62
00:04:38,285 --> 00:04:40,405
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">3月啊 好难等呀</font>

63
00:04:40,715 --> 00:04:41,645
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是啊</font>

64
00:04:42,575 --> 00:04:45,935
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">3月的话 4号就是犬子的生日吧</font>

65
00:04:46,325 --> 00:04:47,455
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">露营的时候搞点活动吧</font>

66
00:04:48,495 --> 00:04:50,095
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小葵也是3月4号生日吗</font>

67
00:04:50,525 --> 00:04:51,265
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我也是啊</font>

68
00:04:51,715 --> 00:04:52,755
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">抚子也是吗</font>

69
00:04:54,435 --> 00:04:56,075
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我们生日一样呢</font>

70
00:04:56,475 --> 00:04:58,015
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是这样呢</font>

71
00:04:58,575 --> 00:05:01,085
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">什么啊 你们俩</font>

72
00:05:01,695 --> 00:05:05,015
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">和大盐平八郎同一天生日啊</font>

73
00:05:07,555 --> 00:05:09,045
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">哟 大盐组合</font>

74
00:05:09,315 --> 00:05:10,605
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">说谁大盐组合呢</font>

75
00:05:12,045 --> 00:05:13,365
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小葵 小葵</font>

76
00:05:14,135 --> 00:05:15,855
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">也带我去伊豆</font>

77
00:05:18,095 --> 00:05:21,815
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这是怎么了 你不是说对露营没兴趣吗</font>

78
00:05:22,155 --> 00:05:24,015
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不是露营 我是想去伊豆呀</font>

79
00:05:24,745 --> 00:05:25,485
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">去看水豚</font>

80
00:05:26,685 --> 00:05:27,745
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">水豚</font>

81
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:32,255
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">第一天在下田海边过夜</font>

82
00:05:32,925 --> 00:05:33,565
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">海滩露营</font>

83
00:05:34,175 --> 00:05:37,435
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">第二天在能看见骏河湾和富士山的山上过夜</font>

84
00:05:38,045 --> 00:05:40,295
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是能看见富士山的露营地哦 小凛</font>

85
00:05:40,705 --> 00:05:41,965
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">知道啦知道啦</font>

86
00:05:42,555 --> 00:05:45,295
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">都是我以前经常和家人去的地方</font>

87
00:05:45,585 --> 00:05:47,355
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">景色都很棒哦</font>

88
00:05:48,125 --> 00:05:51,935
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">其他想去的地方 我们再慢慢商量 怎么样</font>

89
00:05:52,275 --> 00:05:53,485
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">同意</font>

90
00:05:54,365 --> 00:05:54,895
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">对了</font>

91
00:05:55,365 --> 00:05:58,745
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">老师 我妹妹也说想去露营</font>

92
00:05:59,035 --> 00:06:00,525
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我可以带她去吗</font>

93
00:06:01,095 --> 00:06:02,205
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">你说朱莉吗</font>

94
00:06:03,125 --> 00:06:06,775
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">说是伊豆的动物园里有会泡温泉的水豚
(（治愈）水豚温泉（超温馨）)</font>

95
00:06:07,235 --> 00:06:08,935
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好治愈呀</font>

96
00:06:09,275 --> 00:06:11,315
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">香橙温泉看上去好舒服呢</font>

97
00:06:11,665 --> 00:06:13,265
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我也想去看看</font>

98
00:06:13,665 --> 00:06:14,505
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">超可爱</font>

99
00:06:15,045 --> 00:06:18,355
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">只要家长同意 就没问题</font>

100
00:06:18,745 --> 00:06:19,825
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">真的吗</font>

101
00:06:20,255 --> 00:06:22,655
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小犬子也来的话 就是7人了</font>

102
00:06:22,965 --> 00:06:24,165
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好大一家子啊</font>

103
00:06:24,955 --> 00:06:27,965
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">咦 老师的车不是只能坐4人吗</font>

104
00:06:28,645 --> 00:06:30,845
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那剩下两人就得坐凛的小摩托</font>

105
00:06:32,145 --> 00:06:33,025
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是杂技团吗</font>

106
00:06:33,625 --> 00:06:34,815
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">没问题的</font>

107
00:06:35,495 --> 00:06:37,675
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我打算跟我妹妹借小面包车</font>

108
00:06:38,225 --> 00:06:39,235
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这样啊</font>

109
00:06:40,075 --> 00:06:41,015
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那个 老师</font>

110
00:06:42,385 --> 00:06:45,175
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我可以骑小摩托去吗</font>

111
00:06:46,535 --> 00:06:47,725
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小面包车够大家坐的啊</font>

112
00:06:48,765 --> 00:06:53,065
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我本来打算新年骑车去伊豆的</font>

113
00:06:53,695 --> 00:06:54,395
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">最后没去成</font>

114
00:06:55,445 --> 00:06:58,755
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">后来就一直想在伊豆的路上跑一跑</font>

115
00:07:00,445 --> 00:07:01,765
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">骑小摩托啊</font>

116
00:07:02,435 --> 00:07:05,285
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">从身延过去 会很辛苦的</font>

117
00:07:06,125 --> 00:07:08,125
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">凛应该没问题的吧</font>

118
00:07:08,675 --> 00:07:11,315
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">之前都骑车去过滨松和伊那了</font>

119
00:07:11,755 --> 00:07:14,485
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小凛是想做《小摩托车旅行》吧 是吧</font>

120
00:07:14,875 --> 00:07:16,685
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">嗯 是啦</font>

121
00:07:18,235 --> 00:07:19,085
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我知道了</font>

122
00:07:19,395 --> 00:07:21,015
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">可不要勉强哦</font>

123
00:07:21,535 --> 00:07:22,075
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是</font>

124
00:07:22,755 --> 00:07:24,965
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好 能骑小摩托去伊豆了</font>

125
00:07:29,495 --> 00:07:30,215
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好</font>

126
00:07:30,455 --> 00:07:33,285
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">为了去伊豆露营 得加油打工了</font>

127
00:07:33,665 --> 00:07:34,345
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是呀</font>

128
00:07:34,855 --> 00:07:36,145
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我要增加轮班</font>

129
00:07:36,465 --> 00:07:38,435
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">也得加油备考了</font>

130
00:07:39,635 --> 00:07:41,035
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这个到时候再说</font>

131
00:08:17,565 --> 00:08:20,405
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">期末考试 禁止交头接耳</font>

132
00:08:28,035 --> 00:08:30,835
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">伊豆欢迎你 推荐美食与美景 在伊豆让身心焕然一新</font>

133
00:08:38,265 --> 00:08:43,485
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">距离伊豆露营 还有6天 要好好准备哦</font>

134
00:08:48,125 --> 00:08:50,365
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">中午要在下田集合</font>

135
00:08:50,735 --> 00:08:53,195
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那就早点出发从沿岸绕过去吧</font>

136
00:08:53,985 --> 00:08:56,495
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">沿着海边看日出应该不错</font>

137
00:08:58,765 --> 00:09:01,215
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">但是海边风很大的吧</font>

138
00:09:04,945 --> 00:09:08,595
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">之前跑过御前崎 风大得让人受不了</font>

139
00:09:09,195 --> 00:09:09,945
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是吧</font>

140
00:09:10,775 --> 00:09:12,515
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这一带到了冬天</font>

141
00:09:12,545 --> 00:09:15,865
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">会吹起一股强西风 俗称“远洲山风”</font>

142
00:09:16,605 --> 00:09:20,535
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">要跑长途的话 装上挡风板比较好</font>

143
00:09:22,515 --> 00:09:25,125
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我家里应该有闲置的</font>

144
00:09:25,705 --> 00:09:27,885
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">需要的话 下次我带给你</font>

145
00:09:29,245 --> 00:09:32,395
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">还是听爷爷的 去要一个比较好</font>

146
00:09:35,125 --> 00:09:37,605
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">凛 惠那 醒着吗</font>

147
00:09:37,765 --> 00:09:38,595
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">睡了</font>

148
00:09:38,885 --> 00:09:39,595
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">咝呀</font>

149
00:09:39,905 --> 00:09:41,025
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这不都醒着嘛</font>

150
00:09:41,735 --> 00:09:44,215
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">关于犬子和抚子的生日</font>

151
00:09:44,495 --> 00:09:46,015
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">送这个给她们怎么样</font>

152
00:09:48,825 --> 00:09:51,425
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这个不错 价格也不贵</font>

153
00:09:51,745 --> 00:09:52,375
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">对吧</font>

154
00:09:53,025 --> 00:09:54,105
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那就这个吧</font>

155
00:09:54,505 --> 00:09:55,865
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好 决定了</font>

156
00:09:56,375 --> 00:09:59,435
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">明天放学后我就去卡力布看看</font>

157
00:09:59,665 --> 00:10:01,965
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好 明天把钱给你</font>

158
00:10:02,195 --> 00:10:03,225
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">拜托你啦</font>

159
00:10:04,425 --> 00:10:04,995
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好</font>

160
00:10:06,315 --> 00:10:08,245
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">下周要去露营啦</font>

161
00:10:16,195 --> 00:10:16,715
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">露营</font>

162
00:10:18,535 --> 00:10:20,135
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">居然对这词有反应啦</font>

163
00:10:21,355 --> 00:10:25,315
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">抱歉啊 天气还太冷了 你不能去露营</font>

164
00:10:25,915 --> 00:10:27,995
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">等天气暖和了我就带你去</font>

165
00:10:28,345 --> 00:10:30,315
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">现在你要好好在家里待着哦</font>

166
00:10:32,315 --> 00:10:33,635
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">晚安 竹轮</font>

